Here's what sets us apart:


  • UGC Approved Degree Programme, A++ Grade Accreditation by NAAC: Earn a prestigious MBA from a university known for its commitment to top-quality education.


  • Industry-Relevant Curriculum: Acquire the skills and knowledge in demand by employers through a curriculum that adapts to the dynamic business landscape.


  • Flexible Learning: Study at your own pace and convenience with our online platform designed to fit into your busy schedule.


  • Experienced Faculty: Learn from renowned academicians and industry experts who bring real-world insights to the virtual classroom.


  • Global Recognition: Boost your career prospects with an MBA that holds value among employers worldwide.

My team builds an open source FinOps and MLOps tool that helps ML teams multiply the number of ML/AI experiments running in parallel with minimal cloud/infrastructure costs.  Some highlights of the project: •	Runsets - automated run of a number of experiments with configurable datasets, hyperparameter ranges and model versions •	Team and individual ML engineer progress observability •	ML/AI task profiling, bottleneck identification - a simple Python module to collect internal metrics and OptScale to collect cloud metrics to find bottlenecks and correlation •	Optimization recommendations - optimal Reserved Instance and Saving Plan usage, rightsizing, unused resources, cost allocation and more  Github project: https://github.com/hystax/optscale OptScale live demo: https://lnkd.in/erQ2SKqy  I’ll be happy if you can take a look and share your feedback or if the project can be useful for your team - I am open for a quick call to discuss.

Hi A Pabitra Kumar! I am Sridher, Co-Founder of Crio.Do, and an ex-Googler. 


Your background as your job title at your company caught my eye, and I wanted to discuss Crio and ways to enhance one's career in software development. 

 

With a recent boom in product-based tech companies, opportunities for skilled developers has grown over 100% in the last year. Developers with hands-on work-ex in key technologies are able to crack these opportunities and sky rocket their career. But unfortunately, gaining hands-on experience in tech skills that matter is not easy. Online video-based courses and tutorials are not effective.


This is why we launched our Masters Program in Software Development for experienced professionals like yourself.


In this program, you will build multiple production-grade tech projects in an actual developer environment, and learn key Full Stack or Backend skills with real work experience. Throughout your learning journey, you will receive strong support and guidance from experienced Crio mentors.

 

The masters program also comes with personalised career services and assured referrals to help you transition into a top developer role at an exciting startup or tech giant. In fact, developers from Crio have gone on to start successful careers in companies like CRED, Meesho, Grab, IBM, Vogo, Lendingkart and more.

 

I would like to personally invite you to experience our revolutionary way of learning tech. The first week of learning is free. Start the masters program for free, and earn an assured scholarship after the free trial.


Happy learning!

Sridher

Co-Founder Crio.Do
